General.Name: Sitio Royalties Corp.
General.Description: Sitio Royalties Corp. acquires, owns, and manages mineral and royalty interests across premium basins in the United States. The company's portfolio comprising mineral and royalty interests in the Permian basin located in West Texas and southeastern New Mexico; the Eagle Ford basin located in South Texas; the DJ basin located in Northeast Colorado and Southeast Wyoming; and the Williston basin including the Bakken located in North Dakota. The company was founded in 2016 and is headquartered in Denver, Colorado.
